reviews.text: Very good.  Excellent service, would recommend both the pizza and very good salad.
Food is good, price is high and service is so so
One of the best Pizza Expresses at the moment. The chefs here are really at the top of their game and cool perfectly. The staff were get too, especially the manager.

Food quality and taste are up to Pizza Express level, staff is helpful. But, we had food mark on some of the clean plate, sad to say but it did affect the appetite.

Air-conditioning was too strong, almost every table faces the air-conditioning vent right below. Well, it brought the food temperature down quicker and that's not a good thing to be honest, and our bald heads are air-cond shy for some reasons.

Place is comfortable and big enough to accompany large party, located just at the corner of building. Well, if you ought to grab some better deal, try the lunch set on Monday-Friday.
Good food, valuable price, very friendly and professional staff. Good for friends and family gathering.

reviews.text: 舊年年尾於帝國中心的好彩海鮮酒家，壽宴3圍，龍蝦烏冬底龍蝦未熟！最尾幾道菜放涼了！雞開始是凍的！伊麵炒飯都是凍的！連主角壽桃包都是凍的！ 一問之下原來廚房佬一早收曬工！
有兩大全層酒楼，可欣賞落地玻璃全海景，價格合理，惟御皇宴某經理怠客，周日飲早午茶容易揾位，但車埸小泊車請早！
這座位於尖沙咀東部的商業大廈，有中式酒樓，韓式餐館，美式咖啡店，商舖和便利店，更有一間基督教會在地庫。
商場内的 Starbucks 附設的坐位，感覺最優閒舒適。
Elite restaurants, dinner at namo. 5 stars because the bathrooms are beyond amazing! Automatic doors!! I will visit again when im back.
